node.text:

LOCATION UNVEIL - While all the skaters are traveling to the french capital for #RedBullParisConquest , let us introduce you to the spots replicated all together as a unique skate park for what is about to go down. Don't miss out! ⚠️

#paris #trocadero #skate

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Red Bull Skateboarding on August 14, 2021 tagging @el_choubi, and @redbullfrance. May be an image of text that says 'RedBull PARIS CONQUEST MAISON GARE DU NORD The melting house' by Argentinian Leandro Erlich created as part of Paris' 2015 'White Night' to highlight global warming.'.

Photo shared by Red Bull Skateboarding on August 14, 2021 tagging @andrewreynolds, and @fnto. May be an image of text that says 'BERCY The Bercy 5 became an international benchmark of oig gap skating. Longer than Macba's Big 4. 4.'.

Photo shared by Red Bull Skateboarding on August 14, 2021 tagging @crabicrab, and @benjamin_deberdt_photography. May be an image of one or more people, outdoors and text that says 'QUAIS DE SEINE This spot pays homage to the famous riverside banks which prevent the Seine from flooding, and the treacherous shin-height ledges.'.

Photo shared by Red Bull Skateboarding on August 14, 2021 tagging @benjamin_deberdt_photography. May be an image of one or more people, outdoors and text that says '1 LA VAGUE The iconic wave-like tructure by Henri de Miller unveiled in 1989 at Jardin des Halles. rare Parisian transition spot,ripped by Sam Partaix, Olly Todd and Jason Lee. spot,'.

Photo shared by Red Bull Skateboarding on August 14, 2021 tagging @borisproust, and @benjamin_deberdt_photography. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'B/nstitut CURIE 肉 ← CURB DE LUXEMBURG This Parisiar curved-ledge spot requires some people-dodging, as it is located on the bustling Boulevard Saint Michel.'.
Photo by Red Bull Skateboarding on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'RedBull CONQUEST AV PARIS LIVE L AUGUST 18TH LOS ANGELES 8:30AM SAO PAULO 2:30PM LISBON 4:30PM PARIS 5:30PM'.
